examples.example:
```
x-pubsubdb-mappings:
  second_word:
    "@pipe":
      - "{a.output.data.text}"
      - ["{@string.split}", " "]
      - ["{@array.get}", 1]
```

**Object A:**
```json
{
  "output": {
    "data": {
      "text": "hello world"
    }
  }
}
```

**Resulting JSON object:**
```json
{
  "second_word": "world"
}
```
